  "body": "Consider reducing the PVClaimBinderSyncPeriod from 10 minutes down to something more reasonable, so that volumes don't sit around unbound for half an hour if it fails twice.\n\nThis would reduce the impact of issues like https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/issues/21498 until the binder/recycler/provosioner consolidation/refactor is complete.\n\nCC @kubernetes/sig-storage @kubernetes/rh-storage \n",
